snippet.title: Office DisOrders
snippet.description: This is a short video of me playing office Disorders (was politics) on the xbox 360. I'm on day 2 and this was my first attempt. This is actually a really neat game which is pretty funny. The main designer is a chap called Ted Hung but each of the days is scripted by a different writer giving you a different style of humour keeping it fresh. its only 80MS points so support the indie game developers and give it a purchase!
